text: Well, I'm glad to hear from you now. I read your letters every day.
Within every lines, telling words of love.  Ooh~ Every time when I think of you, I know your love for me is true.
Deep in my sweetie, I found my sweet love, Ooh~... Do you still love me now? Do you still need me now?
I keep asking myself what the answer would be. I just want you to know that I do love you so.
So, just whisper to me every single words of love.
